                                    text ever since the 1500s,Lorem Ipsum is
                                    simply dummy text of the printing and
                                    typesetting industry. Lorem Ipsum has been
                                    the industry's standard dummy text ever
                                    since the 1500s,
                                  </p>
                                </div>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        </Accordion.Body>
                      </Accordion.Item>
                    </Accordion>
                  </div>
                </div>
              </Accordion.Body>
            </Accordion.Item>
          </Accordion>
        </div>
      </div>
    </>
  );
};
